data.value:
XNB Modkit GUI is a interface tool for XNB Node by Draivin found at:
https://goo.gl/7NBmij (url shortend for length reasons)
To use the tool, simply navigate the tabs and select the folders. Making the XNB Tool easier to manage outside of the command line quickly and easily.
By: HyperCrusher
